---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="legal-content">
    <h1>How to Delete Your Account and Associated Data</h1>

    <div class="deletion-methods">
      <h2>Method 1: In-App Deletion (Recommended)</h2>
      <p>The fastest way to delete your account and all associated data:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Open the D2 Health Club app</li>
        <li>Go to Settings</li>
        <li>Tap "Update Profile"</li>
        <li>Tap "Delete Account"</li>
        <li>Confirm by tapping "Delete Now"</li>
      </ol>
      <p class="note">
        ⚠️ Once confirmed, your account will be immediately deleted. You will be
        signed out, and we cannot restore your data afterward.
      </p>

      <h2>Method 2: Email Request</h2>
      <p>
        Alternatively, you can request account deletion by sending an email to <a
          href="mailto:support@d2health.club">support@d2health.club</a
        >
      </p>
      <p>
        Our support team will process your request and manually delete your profile
        and all associated data.
      </p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>What gets deleted?</h3>
        <p>Account deletion permanently removes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your user profile</li>
          <li>Step count history</li>
          <li>Achievement records</li>
          <li>Connected gaming accounts</li>
          <li>All other associated data</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .deletion-methods {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .deletion-methods ol {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: #999;
  }

  .deletion-methods li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .note {
    background: rgba(255, 166, 0, 0.1);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    color: #ffa600;
  }

  .info-box {
    background: rgba(67, 222, 194, 0.1);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .info-box h3 {
    color: #43dec2;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .info-box ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: #999;
  }

  a {
    color: #43dec2;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style> 